{"tid":771471,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"地產狗 鄺俊宇 朱凱廸","createTime":"2018-08-08T03:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T13:01:04.000Z","uid":54703,"like":9,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c72a60384fe95d140f82baece7df2703449933b2","tid":771471,"uid":54703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:37:35.000Z","msg":"立法會議員<span style=\"color: red;\">鄺俊宇</span>希望政府「刀下留窰」，又相信與珍貴龍窰活化成社區中心是「美事」，他擔心若政府一意孤行要建屋，打樁工程對龍窰的影響沒有人可百分百估算。另一立法會議員<span style=\"color: red;\">朱凱廸</span>認為，政府在新界西已有多項大型發展計劃，預計新增人口達40萬，若政府繼續在屯門挖走綠化地帶作房屋發展，為屯門區居民帶來不合比例壓力，同時面對新界西醫院床位不足及交通問題，希望政府做好龍窰保育，而非為屯門區市民帶來新增人口壓力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/219242/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E6%96%BC-%E9%9D%92%E5%B1%B1%E9%99%B6%E7%AA%B0-%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%8B-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%86%82%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%B5%90%E6%A7%8B%E4%BF%83%E6%B4%BB%E5%8C%96%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F219242%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2593%25AC%25E6%2596%25BC-%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E9%2599%25B6%25E7%25AA%25B0-%25E9%2599%2584%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E5%25B1%258B-%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2586%2582%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A7%258B%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258C%2596%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595&d=Gwu7UGslcp1keCAvSO4gUHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=227a22ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/219242/%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E6%96%BC-%E9%9D%92%E5%B1%B1%E9%99%B6%E7%AA%B0-%E9%99%84%E8%BF%91%E5%BB%BA%E5%B1%8B-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%86%82%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E7%B5%90%E6%A7%8B%E4%BF%83%E6%B4%BB%E5%8C%96%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95</a>"},{"pid":"c0c81d01d275d446122d6bd3fac0ae216e046355","tid":771471,"uid":43146,"like":11,"dislike":9,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T03:46:00.000Z","msg":"D環保撚保育撚見親政府話搵地起樓